message: Hello! Welcome to Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Hi Chris! I'm pleased with my current policy but have a question about coverage for rental cars.
That's great to hear that you're happy with your policy. I'd be happy to help with your query about rental car coverage. Before we proceed, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Sure, my name is Sarah Jones.
Thank you for completing security, Sarah. Can you also provide me with your date of birth?
Great, thank you. And finally, can you confirm your first line of address and postcode?
My address is 123 Green Street, AB1 2CD.

Perfect, that's all correct. Now, let's look into your query about rental car coverage. A possible resolution could be to add on our optional rental car insurance to your current policy. Does this work for you?
I think that could be a good option for me. How much would that cost?
I can present some options for you based on your current policy. Please allow me a moment to review and provide you with the details.
Thank you for looking into this for me, Chris. I really appreciate your help.
You're welcome, Sarah. I'm glad that I was able to help. I'll get back to you shortly with the information on the rental car coverage.
You are welcome! If you have any other questions in the meantime, please don't hesitate to ask. Have a great day!
